G\">PLG</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.740</biblScope> </bibl>); <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">στάθμα πατρῴα</foreign> perh. the <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">measure</tr_> [of piety] towards his father, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0033.tlg002.perseus-grc1:6:45\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pi.\">Pi.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ P.\">P.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.45</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">στάθμας ἑλκόμενοι περισσᾶς</foreign> perh. straining at an over-exact <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">measure</tr_>, ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0033.tlg002.perseus-grc1:2:90\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.90</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n96174.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">verification, certification</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τὰς ς. τῶν μέτρων ἀπὸ τοῦ βελτίστου ποιεῖσθαι</foreign> prob. in <bibl n=\"Perseus:abo:pap,P.Tebt.:5:88\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ PTeb.\">PTeb.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.88</biblScope> </bibl> <date TEIform=\"date\">(ii B.C.)</date>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n96174.3\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">plummet</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">plumbline</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">μολιβαχθής</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">AP</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.103</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> (<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Phil.\">Phil.</a></author> </bibl>); <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ῥιπτεῖσθαι ἄνω κατὰ στάθμην</foreign> to be thrown perpendicularly upwards, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg005:296b:24\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Cael.\">Cael.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">296b24</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"III\" id=\"n96174.4\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">like</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">γραμμή</ref></xr>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">the line which bounds the racecourse, goal</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">δραμεῖν ποτὶ στάθμαν</foreign>, metaph. of man's life, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0033.tlg003.perseus-grc1:6:7\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pi.\">Pi.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">N.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.7</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">παρ᾽ οἵαν ἤλθομεν ς. βίου</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg010.perseus-grc1:1514\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ion\">Ion</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1514</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n96174.5\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">starting point</tr_>, 'scratch', <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">στάθμης ὁρμηθέντες ἀπόσσυτοι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0023.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:102\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Opp.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ H.\">H.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.102</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg4083.tlg001:1023:5\" default=\"